    <section id="howtoinstall">
      <title>How to install</title>
      <p>1. Install the gem:</p>
      <source>gem install ai4r</source>
      <p>2. Include require statements in your code:</p>
      <source>
require "rubygems"
require "ai4r"
      </source>
